Singapore.title: Number of Bank Accounts for Singapore
Singapore.notes:
Number of depositors with commercial banks per 1,000 adults.

For each type of institution calculated as: (reported number of depositors)*1,000/adult population in the reporting country. (International Monetary Fund, Financial Access Survey)

Source Code: GFDD.AI.01
